{"word":"G1274 - διανύω - dianýō - dee-an-oo'-o - Finish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διανύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dianýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-an-oo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Finish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொடர்"},{"paragraph":"to accomplish fully, bring quite to an end, finish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>anuo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>effect</i>); to <i>accomplish thoroughly:</i> - finish.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}